#### Assignment 1: Linked List Review - Word Ladder Problem

Change one letter at a time to work from one word to another, each word in the middle needs to be valid.

Goal: Find shorted path to change words

Announce when there is no solution

Will have a dictionary file to refer to

##### Two Methods:

Brute Force - Try all possibilities

Greedy Solution - Find Best Moves

##### Tips

Find shortest word with most letter matches

Track used words to avoid cycles (Consider removing them from dictionary).
